1.Stack 
    navigation ke methods 
            .navigate() ---> go to the screen by name
            .goBack()    ----> go to back stacked screen
            .push()    ----> same scrren ko multiple times stack me add kr skte hai  (mtlb agr hum home me hai and then click kiye ja rhe to multiple instance add hoga stack me lekin yhi kam agr hum navigate se krte to nhi hota).  ---> Always add a new instanse

            .replace() ------->replace current screen, means user previous screen pe (back) nhi ja sk ta 
            .popToTop()
            .popTo()


